Help:

1. Preferable Platform: Ubuntu 12.04 + 
2. Perform Update
   $ sudo apt-get update
3. Install Python Setup Tools
   $ sudo apt-get install --force-yes --yes python-setuptools 
4. Install Scapy and DPKG
    $ sudo apt-get install python-scapy
                or
    $ sudo pip install scapy

    $ sudo apt-get install python-dpkt
                or
    $ pip install http://dpkt.googlecode.com/files/dpkt-1.8.tar.gz
5. Ensure your Host has atlease two interfaces (Ex: eth0 and eth1)
6. Run the file smartpcapreplay.py using sudo permissions 
    $ sudo python smartpcapreplay.py

